<br>
I left FV over year ago for many reasons. One of the reasons I left happened tonight and is the reason of this rant. <br>
<br>
Tonight, my current home ( Antonius Bayle Server) was down,  So I came back to good old Firiona Vie. ) <br>
<br>
The reason for this rant is.<br>
<br>
BINDERS CAN ONLY BIND IN CITY ZONES.  <br>
<br>
The ablity of casters to bind anywhere was on any other server but FV was reason number four why I left.<br>
 <br>
<br>
The other reasons were<br>
<br>
1. Unable to play other charactors on this servers ie, Same old druid, day after day. <br>
<br>
2. Unable to store loot (Big problem before extended banking).<br>
<br>
3. TLC<br>
<br>
4.  Unable to Bind anywhere as cast bind anywhere.<br>
<br>
5.  There is a greater number of people than on the other servers that WHINE about the way other folks play.<br>
<br>
6. This Chat board -  While I love reading things posted here,  this board has way too much hate posted here - too many board trolls with matches.<br>
<br>
Ridale Starwind<br>
LV 48 Druid of Karana <br>
<br>
Vytek <br>
LV 46 Enchanter Agnostic - Gods should worship me.)<br>
<br>
<br>
I feel beter already. )<br>
